Type: Package
Package: abstr
Title: Create Transport Scenarios for use in the A/B Street Software
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robin",
           family = "Lovelace",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rob00x@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5679-6536"))
Description: Provides functions to convert origin-destination data,
    represented as straight 'desire lines' in the 'sf' Simple Features
    class system, into JSON files that can be directly imported into the
    A/B Street transport planning/simulation software.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/a-b-street/abstr,
